  "title": "Image Map",
  "description": "Get any image from the internet on a map.",
  "body": "<h2 style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"color: #2dc26b;\"><strong>ImageMap</strong> makes map creation via images from the internet simple.</span></h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><em><strong><span style=\"color: #3cf06e;\">Uses a custom renderer for optimized performance</span></strong></em></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: #b96ad9;\"><em><strong>Premium version is now FREE on Modrinth. Check out <a title=\"ImageMapPlus\" href=\"https://modrinth.com/plugin/image-map-plus\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><span style=\"color: #2dc26b;\">ImageMap<span style=\"color: #e67e23;\">Plus</span></span></a></strong></em></span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<div class=\"spoiler\">\n<div class=\"spoiler-title\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: #f1c40f;\"><strong>How It Works?</strong></span></div>\n<div class=\"spoiler-contents\" style=\"text-align: center;\">\n<p><span style=\"color: #f1c40f;\">1. Find an image that you want to have as a map. Copy the link for the image. The link should look something like this:</span> <span style=\"color: #3598db;\"><code><a href=\"https://images.polymart.org/resource/2916/thumbnail.png\">https://images.polymart.org/resource/2916/thumbnail.png</a></code></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #f1c40f;\">2. Join the server and use the command <span style=\"color: #3598db;\"><code>/im &lt;link&gt;</code> &nbsp;<span style=\"color: #f1c40f;\">Put the image link there. <em><span style=\"color: #e03e2d;\">(Permission Required)</span></em></span></span></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #f1c40f;\"><span style=\"color: #3598db;\"><img src=\"https://polymart-attachments.s3.amazonaws.com/516773f0-39c5-4cfc-87b5-9c9f275edf03/default/attachment.png\" /></span></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #f1c40f;\"><span style=\"color: #3598db;\"><img src=\"https://polymart-attachments.s3.amazonaws.com/351f0772-8edb-4bf9-aee4-d70c94150d43/default/attachment.png\" width=\"360\" height=\"302\" /></span></span></p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<div class=\"spoiler\">\n<div class=\"spoiler-title\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: #3598db;\"><strong>Commands &amp; Permissions</strong></span></div>\n<div class=\"spoiler-contents\">\n<p><span style=\"color: #169179;\">/im &lt;link&gt;</span> - <span style=\"color: #c2e0f4;\">Generates a map with the given image link</span></p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<div><span style=\"color: #95a5a6;\">imagemap.create</span></div>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>",
